@cap_theorem_backend_HostAddress = http://localhost:5112

### Login con Google (redirige a OAuth)
GET {{cap_theorem_backend_HostAddress}}/api/auth/google

### Login con GitHub (redirige a OAuth)
GET {{cap_theorem_backend_HostAddress}}/api/auth/github

### Métricas públicas de landing
GET {{cap_theorem_backend_HostAddress}}/api/landing/metrics
Accept: application/json

### Dashboard del usuario autenticado
GET {{cap_theorem_backend_HostAddress}}/api/dashboard
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Accept: application/json

### Ver credenciales de conexión (registra CREDENTIALS_VIEWED en AuditLog)
GET {{cap_theorem_backend_HostAddress}}/api/databases/credentials
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Accept: application/json
